Matrimid and metal-organic polyhedra–18 (MOP-18) electrospun composite nanofibers were utilized to fabricate free-standing, electrically conducting, and high-energy density hybrid supercapacitor electrodes. Electrospinning multiple compositions of Matrimid and MOP-18 mixture followed...
